OL,3,CMan guilty of stabbing victim multiple
OL,4,Ctimes outside Co-op
OL,6,FA Pewsey man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fgrievous bodily harm after stabbing a
OL,8,Fman multiple times outside a Co-op
OL,9,Fshop.
OL,11,FLuciano Marenghi, 65, of High Street,
OL,12,Fcarried out the attack after an
OL,13,Fargument outside the Co-op in Pewsey
OL,14,Fon 4 September 2023.
OL,16,FMembers of the public were able to
OL,17,Fdetain Marenghi while they waited for
OL,18,Fthe police to arrive.
