OL,6,FInvestigating officer DC Eleanor Darcy
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a nasty incident which
OL,8,Fresulted in the victim suffering
OL,9,Fmultiple stab wounds.
OL,11,F"I'm pleased that (Marenghi) has been
OL,12,Ffound guilty and has been kept in
OL,13,Fcustody ahead of his sentencing.
OL,15,F"I'd like to thank the members of the
OL,16,Fcommunity who came forward during the
OL,17,Fincident to help detain Marenghi and
OL,18,Falso keeping the weapon secure until
OL,19,Fthe emergency services arrived.
